lysis and data, making the volume interesting to a wide audience.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 0aSex differencesxSocial aspectszGreat Britain. 0aSex rolexSocial aspectszGreat Britain. 0aWelfare statexSex differenceszGreat Britain. 0aWelfare statezGreat Britain. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Gender Studies.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertBristol University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2013-1995z9783111196213oZDB-23-BUPP0 cprintz978184742664240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781447314240423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781447314240/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-BUPPc1995d2013